  基于极点到坐标原点的距离函数的常规地图投影分类体系
  Classified System of Routine Map Projection Based on the Distant Function between the Pole to Coordinate Origin
 
</article-title></title-group><contrib-group><contrib contrib-type="author" xlink:type="simple"><name name-style="western"><surname>钟</surname><given-names>业勋</given-names></name><xref ref-type="aff" rid="aff1"><sup>1</sup></xref><xref ref-type="corresp" rid="cor1"><sup>*</sup></xref></contrib><contrib contrib-type="author" xlink:type="simple"><name name-style="western"><surname>胡</surname><given-names>宝清</given-names></name><xref ref-type="aff" rid="aff3"><sup>3</sup></xref><xref ref-type="aff" rid="aff2"><sup>2</sup></xref></contrib><contrib contrib-type="author" xlink:type="simple"><name name-style="western"><surname>边</surname><given-names>少锋</given-names></name><xref ref-type="aff" rid="aff4"><sup>4</sup></xref><xref ref-type="aff" rid="aff2"><sup>2</sup></xref></contrib><contrib contrib-type="author" xlink:type="simple"><name name-style="western"><surname>陈</surname><given-names>成</given-names></name><xref ref-type="aff" rid="aff4"><sup>4</sup></xref><xref ref-type="aff" rid="aff2"><sup>2</sup></xref></contrib><contrib contrib-type="author" xlink:type="simple"><name name-style="western"><surname>康</surname><given-names>丽文</given-names></name><xref ref-type="aff" rid="aff4"><sup>4</sup></xref><xref ref-type="aff" rid="aff2"><sup>2</sup></xref></contrib></contrib-group><aff id="aff3"><addr-line>广西师范学院，北部湾环境演变与资源利用省部共建教育部重点实验室，广西 南宁；广西师范学院，广西地表过程与智能模拟重点实验室，广西 南宁 </addr-line></aff><aff id="aff4"><addr-line>海军工程大学导航工程系，湖北 武汉</addr-line></aff><aff id="aff1"><addr-line>广西师范学院，北部湾环境演变与资源利用省部共建教育部重点实验室，广西 南宁；广西师范学院，广西地表过程与智能模拟重点实验室，广西 南宁；海军工程大学导航工程系，湖北 武汉；广西测绘地理信息局，广西 南宁</addr-line></aff><aff id="aff2"><addr-line>null</addr-line></aff><author-notes><corresp id="cor1">* E-mail:<email>gxzyxun@163.com(钟业)</email>;</corresp></author-notes><pub-date pub-type="epub"><day>22</day><month>12</month><year>2016</year></pub-date><volume>06</volume><issue>06</issue><fpage>459</fpage><lpage>466</lpage><permissions><copyright-statement>&#169; Copyright  2014 by authors and Scientific